item.title: CVE-2015-9196|2024-08-06T08:43:41.167Z -- qualcomm%2C%20inc. -- snapdragon%20mobile%2C%20small%20cell%20soc
item.description: In Android before 2018-04-05 or earlier security patch level on Qualcomm Snapdragon Mobile and Small Cell SoC FSM9055, MDM9635M, SD 400, and SD 800, improper input validation in tzbsp_ocmem can cause privilege escalation.
